Subject: [PATCH v14 12/15] mtd: spi-nor: core: perform a Soft Reset on shutdown
Date:   Thu, 1 Oct 2020 00:27:29 +0530
Message-ID: <20200930185732.6201-13-p.yadav@ti.com>
